# - WordPress plugin (wordpress-plugin/)
# - Universal JavaScript snippet (universal-snippet/)
# - Shared core logic (shared/)
# - Root-level configuration and documentation

# =============================================================================
# Node.js Dependencies
# =============================================================================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# =============================================================================
